    "x": "When you turn on Stocks, you can still spend and send your money any time.\nThe processing times can sometimes be much quicker than written in the table below — we’ll give you a delivery estimate when you set up your transfer.\nFind out how to avoid unexpected processing time\nThe amount you can transfer without this processing time depends where you live, and whether you’re a personal or business customer.\nWhere you live\nPersonal or business customer\nDaily transfer total\nProcessing time\nEEA\nPersonal\n120,000 EUR\nUp to 4 working days\nEEA\nBusiness\n600,000 EUR\nUp to 4 working days\nSingapore\nPersonal\n170,000 SGD\nUp to 6 working days\nSingapore\nBusiness\n850,000 SGD\nUp to 6 working days\nSwitzerland\nPersonal\n100,000 CHF\nUp to 4 working days\nSwitzerland\nBusiness\n500,000 CHF\nUp to 4 working days\nUK\nPersonal\n100,000 GBP\nUp to 4 working days\nUK\nBusiness\n500,000 GBP\nUp to 4 working days\nYour daily transfer total includes money that you:\nsend\nconvert\nmove between Wise currencies and jars\nIt doesn't include spending with your card, ATM withdrawals, scheduled transfers, or direct debits.\nMaking multiple transfers\nYou can make multiple transfers in one day without processing time as long as it’s under"
