    "x": "All Wise personal customers have daily and monthly account spending limits, which is the amount that can be spent by card and withdrawn from ATMs across all cards on your account. You can also choose to set spending limits on specific cards.\nFind out more about your card spending limits\nHow to change your account spending limits\nOn web\nGo to the Cards tab\nSelect\nYour spending limits\nSelect\nEdit\nin the\nAccount limits\nsection\nEnter your new limits, and\nConfirm\nOn the app\nGo to the\nCards tab\nSelect\nYour spending limits\nSelect\nEdit\nin the\nAccount limits\nsection\nEnter your new limits, and\nConfirm\nYou can also view and edit your spending limits on your profile, under\nLimits\n.\nFor US-issued cards, you’ll have different kinds of spending limits, which you can edit individually. You can only change between default and maximum limits.\nHow to manage spending limits for a specific card\nSome US customers can only set new limits for a specific card on web.\nSetting new limits for one of your cards\nOn the web\nGo to\nCards\nSelect the card you’d like to set limits for\nSelect\nSet limits for this card\nEnter the daily and monthly spending limits you’d like to set for this card, and confirm\nOn the app\nGo"
