    "x": "Here's how you can change your business details on either web or app depending on if your business has been verified or not.\nIf your business isn’t verified\nIf your business hasn’t been verified yet, follow these steps to edit your details on either web or app.\nGo on your business name in the top corner — make sure you're in your business account\nSelect\nBusiness details\nSelect\nEdit\nfor the section you need to change and fill in the form\nSelect\nRequest change\nIf your business is already verified\nIf your business has been already verified, you may still be able to\nupdate your name and  address\nby following the steps above, as long as it's within the same country and legal entity. You need the right permissions in your team to be able to edit these details.\nAddress change\nYour trading address should be a permanent physical address. We can’t accept PO boxes or virtual or temporary addresses (hotels, Airbnbs) for a trading address.\nIf your business is changing countries, it's going to change its legal entity, so you would need to open a new business account with Wise.\nName change\nNote that once name change is complete, all statements will display the new name. If you need statements to "
