    "t": "Can I switch between business accounts?",
    "c": "Wise Business",
    "u": "https://wise.com/help/articles/2487047/can-i-switch-between-business-accounts",
    "x": "If you’ve got a business account set up — or you have access to several business accounts — it’s easy to switch between them. Please always make sure to check which account you’re using before creating a transfer.\nWebsite\nOn the website, click on your name / your business name in the top right corner\nSelect the account you'd like to switch to — business or personal\nApp\nYou can switch accounts on the mobile app via the\nYour account\ntab.\nClick on the circle with your profile photo/initials in the top left corner.\nSelect the account you'd like to switch to — other business or personal\nWhat if I can’t see the account I’m looking for?\nIf you can’t see the account you’re looking for when you go to switch, it might be because:\nYou signed up with a different email address for that account. Try logging out, and then logging in again with the right email address.\nYour access may have been revoked.\nContact the account owner or a team member with permission to add or remove team members to get access again."
