    "x": "For most business accounts you can leave your Wise Business account, and transfer it to another team member at any time.\nIf your business is registered in\nJapan\n,\nHong Kong\n, or\nSingapore\n, please check the exceptions below for the procedure.\nHow to change ownership\nYou can only change ownership\non the web\n:\nClick on your business name in the top-right corner\nSelect\nTeam members and payment approvals\nClick your name to go to your team member page\nSelect\nTransfer ownership\n— if you don’t have any other team members, you’ll need to\nAdd a team member\nfirst\nFrom your list of team members, choose the new owner\nSelect\nContinue\nand leave the account\nLearn more about managing your team’s access\nWhat happens once I transfer ownership?\nOnce you transfer ownership of an account, your access is fully cancelled. This means, you can’t log in anymore, and your business Wise cards will be deleted.\nYou can be invited again at any time.\nIf the current account owner isn't available to transfer ownership\nIf the current owner is not available to transfer ownership of the business account, a business director needs to\ncontact us\nand request the change.\nWe’ll need the following information from a directo"
