    "x": "To open a Wise Business account in Hong Kong, we need to verify your identity and your business details.\nWe also need to\nverify your personal information\n, so we’ll ask you to send us a photo of your ID document and in some cases a selfie.\nCurrently, we’re unable to support trusts, charities, and non-profit organisations in Hong Kong.\nWhat do I need to provide to verify my business?\nYou'll need to submit the following information and documents based on your business type:\nSole trader\nBusiness name and address. If you’re operating at a different address, you need to submit it as well\nBusiness category and details of business activities\nBusiness owner’s valid photo ID and information (name, date of birth, country of residence, nationality)\nID with Liveness\nBusiness registration certificate (BR)\nPartnership\nBusiness name and address. If you're operating at a different address, you need to submit that as well\nBusiness category and details of business activities\nPartners’ valid photo ID and information (name, date of birth, country of residence, nationality)\nID with Liveness\nBusiness registration certificate (BR), partnership registration document, or partnership deed\nLimited company\nBu"
